12
00:01:42,417 --> 00:01:43,501
你去啦！妈妈叫你去的啦
Go on.
- Mom asked you to go.

13
00:01:43,584 --> 00:01:46,209
快去啊,快
Hurry!

14
00:01:54,292 --> 00:01:55,876
表姨,妈妈说柴妈妈来了
Auntie, mom says Mrs. Chai is here

15
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,376
叫你快点去
She wants you to go.

16
00:01:57,459 --> 00:01:59,584
去给你介绍男朋友啦
She wants to introduce a guy to you.

17
