跟了你,这一辈子就跟了你了
I married you, and I will be with you forever.

201
00:23:19,751 --> 00:23:24,251
我只是觉得我们还能吃自己的
I just think we should eat our own food.

202
00:23:25,126 --> 00:23:26,959
就不要别人剩的
We don't need leftovers from others.

203
